sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Commit History Webview
participant Router as HistoryMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as OpenHistoryDiffUseCase
participant Repo as GitRepository implements GitHistoryOperations
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime
participant VSCode as VS Code Diff Editor

User->>App: Open file diff
App->>Router: history/openDiff(repositoryLocator, commitHash, filePath, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repo
Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, commitHash, filePath, signal)
UseCase->>Repo: getCommitFileDiff(commitHash, filePath, signal)
Repo->>Runtime: getCommitFileDiff(executionContext, commitHash, filePath, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: getCommitFileDiff(executionContext, commitHash, filePath, signal)
Cli-->>Runtime: readonly left/right content
Runtime-->>Repo: readonly left/right content
Repo-->>UseCase: readonly left/right content
UseCase-->>Router: diff model
Router->>VSCode: openDiff(leftUri, rightUri, title)
VSCode-->>User: Show diff
Router-->>App: history/openDiffResponse(requestId)
